  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aurel.track.beans.base.BaseTMailTemplateDefBean

    TMailTemplateDefBean

    public abstract class BaseTMailTemplateDefBean
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Locale and e-mail type specific template definitions for notification emails You should not use this class directly. It should not even be extended; all references should be to TMailTemplateDefBean
